column3: See [this](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/13366#discussion_r192403908) comment as to why these weren't updated when we did the OS X -> macOS migration in #13366:\n> No need to rename the file every time apple changes the name of the operating system. This will break all external links.
I agree with not renaming files.
